text: Prey Ampok Commune () is a khum (commune) in Kiri Vong District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, Prey Ampok Commune has 9 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable mw-collapsible" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21040801 |Prey Lieb |ព្រៃលៀប |- !2 |21040802 |Khvav |ខ្វាវ |- !3 |21040803 |Trapeang Pring |ត្រពាំងព្រីង |- !4 |21040804 |Amrae |អំរ៉ែ |- !5 |21040805 |Soben |សុបិណ |- !6 |21040806 |Prey Ampok |ព្រៃអំពក |- !7 |21040807 |Thnal Louk |ថ្នល់លោក |- !8 |21040808 |Pump Edth |ពុម្ពអិដ្ឋ |- !9 |21040809 |Chheu Teal Phluoh |ឈើទាលភ្លោះ |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Kiri Vong District
